{"tid":1008393,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"可以點幫食緊抑鬱藥嘅人","createTime":"2019-02-04T12:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T14:46:17.000Z","uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b983cc9bbdf4cd828dd42b1b8253d0a7aafa0005","tid":1008393,"uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:42:56.000Z","msg":"有無過來人可以分享下可以點幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bee68710d326a2ca1619d30fd5f807f3da3870c","tid":1008393,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"提佢食藥<br />\n利 食緊"},{"pid":"64c8241f3e23d6dac188e1f8b29bb54edb1d09bf","tid":1008393,"uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bee68710d326a2ca1619d30fd5f807f3da3870c","tid":1008393,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"提佢食藥<br />\n利 食緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"除咗依樣<br />\n有無其他方面可以幫<br />\n同埋可唔可以講下想人為你做啲咩？"},{"pid":"8120483e137a8d65010a98b13c1f86c8d73e1d23","tid":1008393,"uid":71495,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"我女朋友係，我都仲摸索緊。<br />\n都有少少可以分享：<br />\n1.多啲俾驚喜佢<br />\n2.帶佢去多啲新地方<br />\n3.搵啲細藝或節目令佢分心<br />\n4.聽多啲佢講野唔好一味自己講<br />\n5.當佢有話題同你講果陣唔好一兩句就帶過咗要將佢topic盡可能develop落去"},{"pid":"e6303fa0280df653f56e18b00b5f369c0d56c93a","tid":1008393,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64c8241f3e23d6dac188e1f8b29bb54edb1d09bf","tid":1008393,"uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bee68710d326a2ca1619d30fd5f807f3da3870c","tid":1008393,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"提佢食藥<br />\n利 食緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:06:08.000Z","msg":"除咗依樣<br />\n有無其他方面可以幫<br />\n同埋可唔可以講下想人為你做啲咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"可能我唔算好嚴重<br />\n所以無乜好大需要<br />\n得閒搵吓佢傾計已經好大幫助"},{"pid":"a0d14eb50ebac87ed22f616486e175f99eba6405","tid":1008393,"uid":71495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bee68710d326a2ca1619d30fd5f807f3da3870c","tid":1008393,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"提佢食藥<br />\n利 食緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:16:26.000Z","msg":"提佢食藥唔係個個鐘意。因為佢地本身會覺得自己冇病,你提佢食藥，佢地會覺得你認為佢有病唔係正常人而唔開心。"},{"pid":"cb3d5483b703e27ea91a732546cb01ea4aa9f064","tid":1008393,"uid":69217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"抑鬱症圍爐區（2）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/917893\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/917893</a><br />\n<br />\n搵到依個post 我自己追下先<br />\n唔該曬樓上兩位巴打"},{"pid":"a94714e8c333ca7eb309afcd78deaffb13b1b887","tid":1008393,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:02:16.000Z","msg":"多啲留意佢，私底下check下有無食過量或者無食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n陪多啲佢同俾佢relax，一開頭食應該更加差"},{"pid":"8ab64282b534176a5fe3ddedb25b2dd11e211304","tid":1008393,"uid":38518,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a0d14eb50ebac87ed22f616486e175f99eba6405","tid":1008393,"uid":71495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1bee68710d326a2ca1619d30fd5f807f3da3870c","tid":1008393,"uid":38518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:49:13.000Z","msg":"提佢食藥<br />\n利 食緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T13:16:26.000Z","msg":"提佢食藥唔係個個鐘意。因為佢地本身會覺得自己冇病,你提佢食藥，佢地會覺得你認為佢有病唔係正常人而唔開心。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T14:11:33.000Z","msg":"都要睇你同個病人嘅關係<br />\n但成日就住就住咪仲顯得佢唔正常<br />\n對我嚟講反而拎出嚟講我會舒服啲"},{"pid":"7f70194cc45d9e5def6872f7bcd705f8fccbd269","tid":1008393,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:46:17.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過呢D同腦部病斷唔到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}